    "description": "Decru's Storage Encryption Processor (SEP) is the primary cryptographic and key management engine for Decru DataFort products. Decru DataFort is a wire-speed storage security appliance. DataFort uses hardware-based encryption, authentication, secure access controls, and secure logging to protect networked storage in NAS, SAN, DAS and Tape environments. DataFort can be deployed transparently, with no changes to desktops, servers, applications, or user workflow.",
